sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Primary Agent
  participant Monitor Subagent
  participant Program
  participant LogStream

  User->>Primary Agent: Debug blocking program with monitoring
  Primary Agent->>Monitor Subagent: Spawn with hang detection rules

  activate Monitor Subagent

  Monitor Subagent->>Program: Start execution in background
  activate Program

  par Program execution and monitoring
      Program->>LogStream: Write continuous logs during execution

  and Monitor Subagent watches
      loop Continuous monitoring
          Monitor Subagent->>LogStream: Tail/read recent logs
          Monitor Subagent->>Monitor Subagent: Check hang conditions<br/>(timeout, error patterns, etc.)

          alt Hang conditions met
              Monitor Subagent->>Program: Kill/Terminate (SIGTERM/SIGKILL)
              Monitor Subagent->>Primary Agent: Report hang detected + logs
          else Continue monitoring
              Monitor Subagent->>Monitor Subagent: Wait for next check interval
          end
      end

      alt Program completed normally
          Program->>Monitor Subagent: Exit with status code
          Monitor Subagent->>Primary Agent: Report normal completion + full logs
      end
  end

  deactivate Program
  deactivate Monitor Subagent

  Primary Agent->>User: Return debug results + comprehensive logs
